{% extends 'base.jinja2' %}

{% block content %}
    <section class="inner-main">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h4>FAQ</h4>
      </div>
      <h5>What should I wear?</h5>
      <p>The attire is black-tie optional.</p>
      <h5>Which airport should I fly into?</h5>
      <p>In order of descending convenience: LGA, JFK, EWR.</p>
      <p>LaGuardia Airport is closest; 20–40 minutes from the venue and hotel if traffic is good.
        John F. Kennedy International Airport is 45–60 minutes away. Newark Liberty International Airport is 60–90 minutes away.</p>
      <h5>What time should I arrive?</h5>
      <p>The ceremony begins at 6pm. Please arrive at least 15 minutes early to allow time for parking and
        seating.</p>
      <h5>Is the venue accessible by public transportation?</h5>
      <p>The venue is a 12-minute walk from the Marcy stop on the J, Z, and M subway lines.</p>
      <p>For those staying in Manhattan, there is also a ferry that runs to Williamsburg from 34th Street or Wall Street.</p>
      <h5>Is there parking?</h5>
      <p>The venue has valet parking.</p>
      <h5>Can I bring a plus-one?</h5>
      <p>If your invitation is addressed to you and "guest," you may bring a plus-one. If your invitation is addressed to
        you only, please do not bring a guest.
      <h5>Is it kid-friendly?</h5>
      <p>Children are welcome at the ceremony and reception, if you would like to bring them.</p>
      <h5>Will my dietary restrictions be accommodated?</h5>
      <p>The venue is able to accommodate most dietary restrictions. There will be vegetarian and vegan options.</p>
      <h5>Is it open bar?</h5>
      <p>Yes, there will be an open bar with a selection of beer, wine, and liquor.</p>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
